fr.dudie.nominatim.model

Class Address

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.dudie.nominatim.model.Address

  • public class Address
extends Object
    Represents an address. 
     {
 
     place_id: "46467619"
     licence: "Data Copyright OpenStreetMap Contributors, Some Rights Reserved. CC-BY-SA 2.0."
     osm_type: "way"
     osm_id: "45247695"
     -
     boundingbox: [
         "48.4065589904785"
         "48.4071006774902"
         "-4.52232980728149"
         "-4.52062273025513"
     ]
     polygonpoints: [ ]
     lat: "48.40683015"
     lon: "-4.52147625"
     display_name: "Rue de Fougères, Bellevue, Brest, Finistère, France"
     class: "highway"
     type: "residential"
     -
     address: {
         road: "Rue de Fougères"
         suburb: "Bellevue"
         city: "Brest"
         county: "Finistère"
         country: "France"
         country_code: "fr"
     }
 
 }

    Jérémie Huchet
